{"tid":2451495,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【佛系育兒】孩子用手食飯免洗碗每周洗澡3次　6孩單親媽自訂收工時間省時佛系育兒","createTime":"2021-03-18T06:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T08:38:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b5579be8a927af1d7d024fc7288ae570cf068ac9","tid":2451495,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:53:58.000Z","msg":"照顧大家庭需要付出大量時間，但澳洲一名6孩單親媽卻主張每周幫孩子洗澡3次，用手吃飯免去洗碗的時間，更自訂收工時間，佛系育兒。她宣稱照顧一個大家庭必須節省時間，認為家長們必須有「下班時間」，並揚言︰「我不是孩子的奴隸。」<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，6孩單親媽Constance Hall育有6名孩子，每天照顧孩子的生活非常忙碌，為了節省時間她絞盡腦汁。她為孩子們準備晚餐時，最害怕洗碗，所以她每天三餐準備食物放在大碗中，讓孩子直接用手拿來吃，免去洗碗的時間。<br />\n<br />\n主張孩子一星期洗澡3次<br />\n另外，她認為孩子不需要每天洗澡，只讓孩子每星期洗澡3次，即使他們身體發出臭味仍不理會，<br />\n&quot;我真的沒時間每晚為每人洗澡，我知道保持乾淨能讓他們看起來可愛一點，但少洗澡一日不會死的。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n減少洗澡的時間，洗衣方面也自然減少，她建議家長們為孩子購買一系列彩色衣籃，並在上面貼上每個孩子的姓名，以盛載洗乾淨、晾好的衣服，若孩子想將衣服收進衣櫃，必須自己處理。<br />\n<br />\n家長有「下班時間」<br />\nConstance又表示，每天的「下班時間」是晚上7時半，這個時間過後，孩子要做甚麼必須親力親為，<br />\n&quot;我會告訴他們「我現在不是你們的媽媽，我不在這裡。」我不是孩子的奴隸，現在我正在喝啤酒。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n她坦言照顧一個大家庭需要省時的方法，將時間留給真正重要的事情，照顧6名孩子不能提供給獨生子女一般高質的生活，<br />\n&quot;你們可以說我是懶惰的媽媽，但與6個孩子同住，所有想法就會改變。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2904593/lazymom_thumb_20210318_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2904593%2Flazymom_thumb_20210318_S_1024.jpg&h=3994d545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2904593/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2904593%2F1_1024.jpg&h=71d59a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2904593/3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2904593%2F3_1024.jpg&h=11892f42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2904593/6_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2904593%2F6_1024.jpg&h=0ca69c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2904593/7_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2904593%2F7_1024.jpg&h=d13045d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f510e30ffd4415d0ca64a659a2709f499a5b4a6d","tid":2451495,"uid":16004,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"呢啲係咪叫無乸教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a4a62fbd6338f71e3990db18a9fbe2f7918073","tid":2451495,"uid":24884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"地方媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8afe32dfee31c8cde7a3a08ac471a3c475a058","tid":2451495,"uid":154505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"呢班細路最後會堅強成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8772200576b38d85a23d8332a4882269969e1ee","tid":2451495,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"咁你又生？<br />\n建議仔女一到18歲就離職唔再做仔女 唔好畀家用"},{"pid":"57d8267ce8d1ed937dcf526cc01a03755a24b231","tid":2451495,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"單親就無計<br />\n除非食政府緩助金咪大把時間<br />\n但有個望落有八歲可以教下佢幫細妹沖<br />\n或教佢幫手洗衫分D工作比佢減輕負擔"},{"pid":"67223add92e45d35d2c03662654b69d33fa682fe","tid":2451495,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫啲仔女著住衫沖涼<br />\n<br />\n可以慳番洗衫時間"},{"pid":"0fe1b205294721e16e6cd90b9027c8cf0dc51ab5","tid":2451495,